Description:
Exciting Possibilities in Enviable Location
Brilliantly situated on a north oriented corner site offering close proximity to Smith and Johnson Streets' vibrant shops and cafes and the CBD, this single level solid-brick contemporary residence represents an exciting renovation or redevelopment opportunity
with the possibility of constructing up to 3 town-residences (STCA).
Currently in completely comfortable condition, it features wide entrance hall through to living/study, light-filled living and dining room boasting vaulted ceilings and a capable kitchen opening out to private north-facing garden. Six spacious bedrooms (BIRs) are complemented by two bright bathrooms and laundry. Also features RC/air-conditioning and OSP.
An outstanding inner urban opportunity.
Leonard Teplin : 0402 431 657

Description:
'Islington Apartments' Twice the Size You'd Expect
More than meets the eye, this 2nd floor 2 bedroom 2 bathroom security apartment is designed to set your spaces apart.
Sleek and stylish, this spacious sensation enjoys open plan entertaining, dynamic granite kitchen (s/steel appliances including dishwasher), balcony terrace with views of leafy Victoria Parade and the city, 2 large bedrooms (one with BIRs), 2 vogue bathrooms with granite benchtops (ensuite) and Euro laundry.
Dressed with monochromatic tones, this sizzling stylemaker features R/C air conditioning, double glazing, intercom, lift access and security basement parking for two cars.
On the edge of the Victoria Street buzz with a fabulous selection of cafes and restaurants, metres to the city tram.

Description:
Perfect Choice
Situated so close to everything you may need this is the ideal home for both investors and first home buyers. Only a stones throw from the CDB, universities, hospitals and trendy Smith & Brunswick Street precincts.
-Security entrance
-Large open plan kitchen, meals and living area.
-Extra cupboard space in kitchen
-Sunny spacious balcony
-Central bathroom with extra large shower and laundry
-Main bedroom with built in robes
-Two split system heating/cooling units
-Secure car parking off street
With many great features including a northerly aspect for extra light and a position providing the ultimate convenience this will go quick, book your inspection today.
